## 16. Production Readiness Checklist

### Infrastructure

- [ ] Multi-region K8s clusters deployed (US-EAST, EU-WEST, AP-SOUTH, AP-EAST)
- [ ] Global Anycast DNS configured with health checks (30s TTL)
- [ ] Envoy ingress with WSS termination and TLS 1.3
- [ ] Redis Cluster per region (6 nodes, 3 shards, cross-AZ)
- [ ] Kafka multi-region with MirrorMaker 2
- [ ] CockroachDB / PostgreSQL with cross-region replication
- [ ] coturn cluster per region with NLB (UDP + TCP)
- [ ] Network policies restricting inter-pod communication

### Security

- [ ] JWT authentication on WebSocket handshake (RS256)
- [ ] Per-call authorization with block/privacy checks
- [ ] TURN credentials: ephemeral, HMAC-SHA1, 24h TTL
- [ ] IP reputation scoring and auto-blocking
- [ ] Rate limiting at Envoy (L7) and application layers
- [ ] DDoS protection (Shield Advanced / Cloud Armor)
- [ ] SRTP media encryption verified
- [ ] SDP/ICE payload size limits enforced
- [ ] Nonce-based replay attack prevention
- [ ] coturn: denied-peer-ip for private ranges
- [ ] TURN secret rotation schedule (90-day)
- [ ] Penetration test completed

### Scalability

- [ ] Stateless WS gateway pods (zero in-memory state)
- [ ] HPA configured: WS pods (15K conn target), coturn (70% allocation target)
- [ ] Graceful pod draining with staggered client reconnect
- [ ] Redis sharding verified for 10M concurrent users
- [ ] Cross-region signaling latency <133ms verified
- [ ] Load tested: 1M concurrent connections per region
- [ ] Load tested: 100K call initiations in 60 seconds

### Observability

- [ ] OpenTelemetry collector deployed per region
- [ ] Distributed tracing for full call lifecycle
- [ ] Metrics: Prometheus → Mimir (long-term storage)
- [ ] Logs: structured JSON → Loki
- [ ] Call quality telemetry pipeline: Kafka → ClickHouse
- [ ] Grafana dashboards: connections, call rate, latency, error rate, TURN usage
- [ ] Alerting: PagerDuty integration for P1/P2 alerts
- [ ] SLO dashboards: 99.995% availability, <120ms call setup

### Reliability

- [ ] Chaos experiments scheduled and passing
- [ ] Redis Sentinel/Cluster failover tested
- [ ] Region failover tested (DNS cutover <60s)
- [ ] Thundering herd prevention (exponential backoff + jitter)
- [ ] Call state auditor CronJob running (orphan cleanup)
- [ ] Split-brain detection and reconciliation
- [ ] Graceful degradation: audio-only fallback on bandwidth constraint
- [ ] Circuit breakers on TURN and cross-region paths

### Operations

- [ ] Runbooks for all P1 alert scenarios
- [ ] On-call rotation established
- [ ] Deployment: blue-green with canary (5% → 25% → 100%)
- [ ] Feature flags for call features (LaunchDarkly / custom)
- [ ] TURN secret rotation automated
- [ ] Certificate rotation automated (Let's Encrypt / ACM)
- [ ] Cost monitoring dashboards with anomaly alerts
- [ ] Capacity review scheduled (monthly)
